c引擎比少差唔多2000蚊牌費，又慳返一大筆錢。<br />\n4：機件設備<br />\nAE110作為一架90年代尾 汽車科技仲未去到非常發達嘅時間推出，AE110冇好似而家最新嘅車咁咁多電子野，簡簡單單嘅電子設備已經足夠咁多駕駛人士使用，又可以慳返一大筆錢唔洗整咁多電子嘢。另外，大家都知道豐田車好耐用，所以大家都唔洗擔心AE110會好似其他德國車咁成日壞呢樣個樣。<br />\n總括而言，AE110係各方面都屌打晒其他對手，應該可以做新嘅連登神車￼"},{"pid":"5b413a989fd2b4b0b05516cd590e716754b5df0a","tid":1073082,"uid":34368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:13:11.000Z","msg":"kia"},{"pid":"69144f794293ab15e308cc1b8f20ed806727b976","tid":1073082,"uid":120918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:13:14.000Z","msg":"ae86"},{"pid":"6e4d54419347e216b86986e36bbeaf4a403e2c8e","tid":1073082,"uid":132189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:13:45.000Z","msg":"TIGUAN"},{"pid":"3a4b17476c835490d2caa99f14a4b03f5e8c46ba","tid":1073082,"uid":92278,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:16:51.000Z","msg":"Alfa Romeo"},{"pid":"25f66bcbfece70264269206fa07d82e6b642abb8","tid":1073082,"uid":37458,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:20:22.000Z","msg":"性價比高？ 認真答你 golf r"},{"pid":"0ee6f1aca375942b4d246f21ec3a177d00e313bc","tid":1073082,"uid":94315,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:25:00.000Z","msg":"Model Y"},{"pid":"531fe8a0593017d813235bfd1b3d875f8a2263a1","tid":1073082,"uid":37107,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"d5f378d5a2c0abff180648189b95f54576ff9eaf","tid":1073082,"uid":37107,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5acd8ff9fb0d01cd99d402436ed343f4894bc954","tid":1073082,"uid":80336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:08:11.000Z","msg":"最近考咗車 諗住買部車玩下<br />\n但睇車睇左一排 冇一款啱心水<br />\n酒肉朋友只係識林寶麥拿倫呢d mk貴車<br />\n完全對車冇研究<br />\n價錢 耗油量 扭力 實用性完全唔識 馬力幾大又唔識<br />\nPolo golf 都有望過下 <br />\n有冇ching 有心得係性價比高既車可以分享下<br />\n2手車 新車都想知多少少"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:10:53.000Z","msg":"GOLF R"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:32:23.000Z","msg":"